thread.title_full: Auto Europe Australia reviewed by John+owen

author: John+owen
title: John+owen
text:
i have always had excellent service, either through internet bookings or by phone. I use Auto Europe for both Australian and overseas car hire and have never been let down.
I find the web site one of the easiest to use and love their prices.
I have been using Auto Europe for years and will continue to as long as I need to hire cars anywhere in the World.
